<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Ready to move up a tier?</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">Take the deeper Gap Assessment, book a paid AI Audit, or talk to Bill directly about what your tier should do next.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/quiz" class="btn-p">Take the Gap Assessment &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/services/ai-audit" class="btn-g">See the AI Audit</a>
